    "description": {
      "en": {
        "provenance": "imported",
        "value": "The program’s interventions target mobile populations, injecting drug  users and men who have sex with men, as well as people who are  HIV-positive. Under the program, prevention efforts and community  outreach through peer education and interpersonal communication will be  scaled up to reduce the stigma related to HIV and to lower the barriers  to accessing HIV and AIDS treatment and counseling services."
